<p>Since 2008, we've been training some of the region's top hockey players as they prepare for their upcoming seasons.</p>

<p>There have been dozens of professional, NCAA/CIS (both male and female), and OHL level players through our doors, not to mention hundreds of Junior and minor hockey players who have all taken on the challenge of a serious, properly structured strength and conditioning program. </p>

