  <img class="alignright" src="/assets/images/platzmassage.jpg" />

  <p>Unlike 10 years ago, itâ€™s no longer just about the training. Nutrition and recovery are now crucial components to an athleteâ€™s development plan and our 2018 program will provide support on both fronts.</p>

  <p>Athletes will be required to fill out a nutrition logs which will be evaluated by the NLPT coaching and therapy staff, who will then provide feedback and structured guidance on developing sound athlete-centered nutrition habits. Additionally, pre and post-workout Biosteel supplementation will be provided for each training session.</p>

